entry.source: Vodyanik are demons that scavenge sunken{F801}ships for treasure. These Vodyanik have been{F801}searching the Ameyoko areas in Ueno. Since{F801}there aren't any sunken ships there, they've{F801}been coming up on land. Exterminate these{F801}Vodyanik and {F804,5}other pirate hordes{F804,0} for a reward!{F801}
